title: Michael Bolton - Timeless (The Classics) 2001
description:
Timeless: The Classics is an album of cover versions by Michael Bolton. It was no.1 on the Billboard charts when it was released. After a rather long chart run the album has been certified 4x Platinum in the US and has sold over nine million copies worldwide. (wikipedia.org)
